description: It's the battle of the beautiful losers. Derrek Diamond was defeated by Lee Stephens, and Brandon Monroe was defeated by Brynn Wyson. Derrek and Brandon return with a chance to dominate someone. Brandon starts off extremely aggressive and in control. Derrek is quiet but tough and he has a plan. Both of these studs are going at it for real for chance to spank and fuck the loser.
title: Derrek Diamond vs Brandon Monroe
